First, consider the section of the rope to the left of where Paul is standing. We have a right triangle formed by the vertical pole, the ground, and this section of the rope, with the rope acting as the hypotenuse.

[asy]
draw((0,0)--(5,0)--(5,3)--(0,3)--cycle,black+linewidth(1));
